2003-02-20  Martin Grabmueller  <mg@glug.org>

	* Cleaned up for release.

2002-08-15  Martin Grabmueller  <mg@glug.org>

	* scanner.c (ttl_next_token): Allow `!' and `?' in identifiers,
	not only at the end.
	(ttl_next_token): Continue processing after skipping invalid
	characters in input.

2002-07-11  Martin Grabmueller  <mg@glug.org>

	* emit-c.c (ttl_emit_c): Emit calls to ttl_register_root() for all
	global variables.

	* libturtlert.h, libturtlert.c: New function ttl_register_root()
	and support core in garbage_collect() for registering global
	variables as GC roots.

	* README: Added file descriptions and build instructions.

2002-05-08  Martin Grabmueller  <mg@glug.org>

	* symbols.c (ttl_symbol_print): Cleanup.

	* symbols.h: Commenting.

2002-04-29  Martin Grabmueller  <mg@glug.org>

	* error.h, error.c: Cleanup and new comments.

	* types.h, types.c, compiler.c: Removed type of kind
	`type_unknown'.

	* compiler.h: Cleanup and commenting.

